setAuthType(String) - Method in class org.vthink.lib.jrouteros.core.auth.AuthService
There are 4 (four) type that are valid, direct, xml, and sqllite.
If you write direct then you just access one time QueryService for accessing MikroTik API.
If you write xml, you have to specify path of xml file that you've created before with method AuthService.setXMLPathFile(String).
If you write properties, you have to specify path of properties file that you've created before with method AuthService.setPropertiesPathFile(String)
